This paper deals with the problem of multi-agent optimization in the presence of communication failures, which is a core topic in the field of multi-agent systems (MAS). Therefore, the most likely category is cs.MA (Multiagent Systems). The paper also involves distributed optimization algorithms, which are often studied in the category of cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing). The paper also deals with the reliability of communication links, which is a topic in the category of cs.SY (Systems and Control). Additionally, the paper involves networked systems, which is a topic in the category of cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). Finally, the paper involves convergence analysis, which is a topic in the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning).
